title: 8 The Power of Belief – How World Class Athletes Outperform the Competition
description: Welcome to the solo round! I plan to interview a number of inspiring business minds, world class athletes, and influential celebrities throughout this entire podcast, but today, I'm going in the ring solo. This is a test to see if both you and I enjoy this format. Perhaps I'll do more in the future like this if you […]
